Interface IReceiptManagerService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ReceiptManagerService

    public interface IReceiptManagerService
    The Interface IReceiptManagerService.

    Warning: DO NOT reference the core.service package classes directly as these are missing the required business functionalities. Use core.facade or ui.service classes instead.

    Author:
    Paydiant Inc.
